15-16<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">13. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106261\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106261)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106261)\">Num. 24:4,16<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">14. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110906\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110906)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110906)\">1 Ne. 2:1<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">15. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115499\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115499)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115499)\">D&amp;C 107:55-56<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">16. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116990\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116990)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116990)\">Abr. 1:26<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">17. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113486\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113486)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113486)\">D&amp;C 27:12<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">18. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115718\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115718)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115718)\">D&amp;C 116:1<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>"}